name: petrol, unleaded, burned in machinery | petrol, unleaded, burned in machinery | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/14889/documentation

This dataset represents the combustion of 1 kg petrol, unleaded, in an unpecified agricultural motor machinery. This dataset is extrapolated from the operation of an agricultural tractor with two tyre-trailers of maximum 8t loading capacity each. Mean velocity when loaded is 15 km/h and mean velocity when empty is 25 km/h.  Emissions and heat waste to the air from combustion and the emission to the soil from tyre abrasion during the transport are included.

This activity starts with consumption of petrol for use in machinery.

Included processes are petrol use and emissions from combustion. 
This activity ends with the combustion of petrol in machinery.
